48
00:02:14,160 --> 00:02:16,400
I think it's definitely formal.

49
00:02:16,400 --> 00:02:17,880
There are many others.

50
00:02:17,880 --> 00:02:21,080
I think this one was just one of the ones that was selected

51
00:02:21,080 --> 00:02:22,560
